
### 3. **.gitignore File**

The **.gitignore** file ensures that unnecessary files (like system files or dependency folders) are not tracked by Git.

```gitignore
# Node modules (if using Node.js or any package manager)
node_modules/

# Logs
*.log

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE or Editor folders
.idea/
.vscode/

# Build or distribution directories
/dist/
/build/
/public/

# Local environment files
.env

